---

## 7. DMS Integration Rules

1. DMS expiry notifications connect to global engine in **ERP DMS.8A** only.
2. DMS must not directly process `erp_email_queue`.
3. Bridge helpers are in `src/server/actions/notifications/bridges/dms-notification-bridge.ts` (admin-manual only).
4. `dms_notification_queue` remains until DMS.8A migrates its records.

---

## 8. Email Settings Integration

1. Email provider is consumed by the global notification/email delivery engine.
2. Feature modules must not call the email provider directly.
3. `isEmailFeatureEnabled(featureCode)` gates must be checked before auto-sending.

---

